    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s in absolute pristine condition\u2014basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
