    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This collector-grade vehicle is presented in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The original paint maintains a deep, mirror-like luster entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a true time capsule; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the interior retains its factory-fresh aroma. Every feature, including the high-fidelity sound system and all electronic assists, operates exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is flawless, supported by a complete binder of authorized dealership service records. The alloy wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread. This is an uncompromising example for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
